- cs.IR (Information Retrieval): The paper deals with retrieving information from photos to estimate air pollution, which could be relevant to this sub-category. 
- cs.MM (Multimedia): The paper involves analyzing and processing multimedia data (photos) to estimate air pollution, which could be relevant to this sub-category. 
- cs.CY (Computers and Society): The paper addresses a societal issue (air pollution) and proposes a novel approach to monitoring it, which could be relevant to this sub-category.
